welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Orting, a charming city known for its beautiful views of Mt. Rainier and small-town charm. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that our city has to offer!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at McChord AFB Airport serves both commercial and military flights.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at McChord AFB Airport is exclusively for military personnel and their families.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Industrial Airport serves domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Industrial Airport handles all freight and shipping operations.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport is the largest and busiest terminal, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: North Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The North Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport is a satellite terminal primarily used for Alaska Airlines flights.

terminals.name: South Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The South Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport is a satellite terminal primarily used for international flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Renton Airport handles all commercial flights and houses various amenities for passengers.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Renton Airport caters to private and charter flights, providing a more exclusive and personalized experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport for all passengers.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport, serving domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The south terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport, primarily used for private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
